      <title>Re: VATHandler Error when editing product</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/xrowecommerce/forum/bug_tracker/vathandler_error_when_editing_product/re_vathandler_error_when_editing_product2</link>
      <description>Found the problem in extension/xrowecommerce/settings/shop.ini.append.php:&#13;
&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
   Handler=xrowecommerce&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
should be&#13;
&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
   Handler=xrowECommerce&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
as per the class name in extension/xrowecommerce/vathandlers/xrowecommercevathandler.php:&#13;
&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
  class xrowECommerceVATHandler&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
This was fixed on 26/05/2011 in SVN, but I couldn't install the package directly from SVN so it got downloaded from xrow, which means their online repository is out of date.</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Geoff Bentley)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/xrowecommerce/forum/bug_tracker/vathandler_error_when_editing_product/re_vathandler_error_when_editing_product2</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Oct 2011 08:16:43 +0000</pubDate>
