    <item>
      <title>insertmedia.js</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/xrowecommerce/forum/bug_tracker/insertmedia_js</link>
      <description>Hi Guys,&#13;
&#13;
Just migrating a site across to xrowcommerce and cam across this issue.&#13;
&#13;
I use a lot of flash in Frontpage billboards for rolling slideshows etc. When I moved stuff accross the flash simply would not show. Traced it down to the fact that it could not find insertmedia.js which is called in content/datatype/view/ezmedia.tlp&#13;
&#13;
I simply added &#13;
&#13;
JavaScriptList[]=insertmedia.js&#13;
&#13;
to the siteaccess design.ini.apend.php and all was fine.&#13;
&#13;
I think if you embed flash it uses a different template that does not call insertmedia.js, so this will only be apparent if you insert flash into billboards.&#13;
&#13;
Great stuff otherwise.&#13;
&#13;
Richard&#13;
&#13;
</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Richard Lundberg)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/xrowecommerce/forum/bug_tracker/insertmedia_js</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Aug 2010 16:30:30 +0000</pubDate>
    </item>
